{
  "stem": "11144.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was one time that I had with my legs that I couldn't walk, that we had to run away there, because they were afraid that if the Germans come to the village, everybody's going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So again, this, the winter structure, was built in the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it had to be-- you know, it had to be for a person to practically stand up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe a little--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, it was maybe for 20 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, there was an opening on the top for the fire, because that was the only way for us to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you slept-- they built from the-- from a trees-- you know, like from 10 trees, they built like kind of a benches or whatever that you slept on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a few times, we had to-- we ended up there-- to sit through that scary part of time, when they were telling us the Germans are coming into the villages.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did they find out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did they know about it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were you with the original group all the time?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Groups?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the villages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember any children in those-- in the house that we stayed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the villages, where we stayed, I guess there were some other families that were hidden.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember particular about a girl who I was friendly with-- again, I don't remember anybody's name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was hidden under a down quilt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the quilts are not like quilts that we know them today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was like a big, you know, thick-- maybe this-- this thick.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
